explanation: "\u25cf\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 Demographic trap: Applies to a country whose population is growing rapidly due to a high birth rate and low death rate.\n\u25cf\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 To escape the demographic trap, countries need to lower fertility rates.\n\u25cf\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 Promoting family planning and contraception reduces birth rates, helping to stabilize population growth and reduce pressure on resources.",
