explanation: "Walter Reed demonstrated the mosquito transmission of yellow fever. Edward Jenner pioneered smallpox vaccination. James Lind showed prevention of scurvy using citrus fruits, and Ronald Ross identified Anopheles mosquitoes as vectors of malaria. Thus, the correct matching is 1-b, 2-c, 3-a, 4-d.",
