explanation: "High-yield notes:<br><br>Magnesium RDA (adults):\nAdult male: \\~400\u2013420 mg/day\nAdult female: \\~310\u2013320 mg/day\nFor single best answer MCQs, the accepted value is \\~400 mg/day\n \nMagnesium is a cofactor for ATP-dependent reactions, neuromuscular stability, and PTH secretion<br><br>\ud83d\udccc Deficiency \u2192 neuromuscular irritability, hypocalcemia, hypokalemia.<br><br><img src=\"https://corebtr-assets-production.s3.ap-south-1.amazonaws.com/question_explanation/39754a3d-3447-414b-b2ec-84b03fc82c7b.jpg\" alt=\"Uploaded Image\">",
