text: "A public health officer is outlining the responsibilities of a male health worker in a community health center. Which of the following are included in the job duties of a male health worker?<br><br>1.\tSputum collection\n2.\tORS distribution\n3.\tDOTS supervision\n4.\tGrowth monitoring\n5.\tEnvironmental sanitation<br><br>Use the following key to mark the correct answer:",
