explanation: "**Duties of a Male Health Worker (MPW-Male) \u2013 PSM**<br><br>Included responsibilities:<br><br>1. **Sputum collection**\n<br>\n    \u2013 Under **NTEP (TB control)**\n2. **ORS distribution**\n<br>\n    \u2013 Diarrheal disease control, outreach activities\n3. **DOTS supervision**\n<br>\n    \u2013 Treatment supervision for TB patients\n4. **Environmental sanitation**\n<br>\n    \u2013 Water safety, waste disposal, vector control activities<br><br>**Male Health Worker \u2192 TB, sanitation, chlorination, surveillance, ORS**<br><br>**Female Health Worker \u2192 MCH, growth monitoring, immunization**",
