explanation: "ICD-11 includes a traditional medicine chapter, reclassifies gender incongruence outside mental disorders, became effective from 1 Jan 2022, and Chapter 6 covers mental, behavioral, and neurodevelopmental disorders. It is also digitally adaptable, making option A (1\u20134) correct.",
