subcategory: "06-health-programmes",
tags: [],
text: "Identify the correctly matched pair of health-related observance and date:",
options: [{"id": "A", "text": "World TB Day \u2014 28 March", "is_correct": false}, {"id": "B", "text": "World Health Day \u2014 7 April", "is_correct": true}, {"id": "C", "text": "World Population Day \u2014 21 July", "is_correct": false}, {"id": "D", "text": "World AIDS Day \u2014 1 November", "is_correct": false}],
explanation: "World Health Day is observed on 7 April, marking the founding of WHO in 1948. Other options are incorrect:<br><br>* World TB Day is on 24 March,\n* World Population Day is on 11 July,\n* World AIDS Day is on 1 December. Hence, option B is the only correctly matched pair.",
