explanation: "Anemia Mukt Bharat includes 1) iron-folic acid supplementation, 2) behavior change communication, 3) digital hemoglobin testing, and 4) bi- annual deworming (done on 10 Feb and 10 Aug), not biennial deworming.<br><br><img src=\"https://corebtr-assets-production.s3.ap-south-1.amazonaws.com/question_explanation/2087fb72-3dc6-4b80-9a17-b4a89f12e5c5.png\" alt=\"Uploaded Image\">",
