explanation: "As per the **amended MTP Act (2021)**, termination up to **20 weeks** requires the opinion of **one registered medical practitioner**.\nFor pregnancies **between 20\u201324 weeks**, the opinion of **two registered medical practitioners** is mandatory for specified categories of women.",
